  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "header"
   },
   "source": [
    "# 🎮 PonyTown 一键部署到Google Colab\n",
    "\n",
    "**6年前的多人在线游戏，5分钟内在线体验！**\n",
    "\n",
    "![Game](https://img.shields.io/badge/Game-READY_TO_PLAY-brightgreen)\n",
    "![Platform](https://img.shields.io/badge/Platform-Google_Colab-orange)\n",
    "![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-FULLY_WORKING-success)\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🚀 特色\n",
    "\n",
    "- 🌐 **无需本地安装** - 直接在Google Colab运行\n",
    "- 🔗 **公网访问** - 使用ngrok映射，任何人都可访问\n",
    "- ⚡ **5分钟部署** - 点击运行即可\n",
    "- 🎯 **零配置** - 所有依赖自动安装\n",
    "- 🎮 **完整游戏** - 2D像素多人在线RPG\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📋 使用方法\n",
    "\n",
    "1. 点击上方的 **\"Open in Colab\"** 按钮\n",
    "2. 按顺序运行下面的代码块\n",
    "3. 等待ngrok公网链接生成\n",
    "4. 点击链接开始游戏！\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "step1"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 步骤1：安装系统依赖"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "install-deps"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 🔧 安装Node.js 18 (Colab兼容版本)\n",
    "import os\n",
    "import subprocess\n",
    "import time\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"🔧 安装Node.js和依赖...\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 安装Node.js 18\n",
    "!curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_18.x | sudo -E bash -\n",
    "!sudo apt-get install -y nodejs\n",
    "\n",
    "# 检查版本\n",
    "!echo \"✅ Node.js版本:\"\n",
    "!node --version\n",
    "!echo \"✅ npm版本:\"\n",
    "!npm --version\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ 系统依赖安装完成！\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "step2"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 步骤2：安装ngrok并设置公网访问"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "setup-ngrok"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 🌐 安装和配置ngrok\n",
    "print(\"🌐 安装ngrok...\")\n",
    "\n",
    "!pip install pyngrok\n",
    "!wget https://bin.equinox.io/c/bNyj1mQVY4c/ngrok-v3-stable-linux-amd64.tgz\n",
    "!tar xzf ngrok-v3-stable-linux-amd64.tgz\n",
    "!chmod +x ngrok\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ ngrok安装完成！\")\n",
    "print(\"ℹ️  如果你有ngrok账户，可以在下一个单元格中添加authtoken以获得更稳定的连接\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "ngrok-auth"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 🔑 可选：设置ngrok authtoken (推荐)\n",
    "# 访问 https://dashboard.ngrok.com/get-started/your-authtoken 获取免费token\n",
    "\n",
    "# NGROK_TOKEN = \"your_token_here\"  # 取消注释并替换为你的token\n",
    "# !./ngrok authtoken {NGROK_TOKEN}\n",
    "# print(\"✅ ngrok authtoken已设置\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"ℹ️  跳过authtoken设置，使用免费临时隧道\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "step3"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 步骤3：下载并配置PonyTown游戏"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "download-game"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 🎮 下载PonyTown Ready版本\n",
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"🎮 下载PonyTown游戏...\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 清理并创建工作目录\n",
    "!rm -rf pony-town-ready\n",
    "!git clone https://github.com/Ritori2022/pony-town-ready.git\n",
    "\n",
    "# 进入目录\n",
    "os.chdir('/content/pony-town-ready')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ PonyTown下载完成！\")\n",
    "print(f\"📁 当前目录: {os.getcwd()}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 检查关键文件\n",
    "!echo \"📋 检查关键文件:\"\n",
    "!ls -la package.json pony-town.js README.md canvas-mock.js mock-login.html"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "step4"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 步骤4：安装游戏依赖"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "install-game-deps"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 📦 安装游戏依赖\n",
    "print(\"📦 安装游戏依赖包... (这可能需要2-3分钟)\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建必需的目录\n",
    "!mkdir -p logs\n",
    "\n",
    "# 安装依赖 (使用适合Colab的参数)\n",
    "!npm install --legacy-peer-deps --ignore-scripts --no-audit --no-fund\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ 游戏依赖安装完成！\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 检查关键依赖\n",
    "!echo \"🔍 检查关键依赖:\"\n",
    "!ls node_modules/ | grep -E \"express|mongoose|passport\" | head -5"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "step5"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 步骤5：启动游戏服务器 + ngrok隧道"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "start-server"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 🚀 启动游戏服务器和ngrok隧道\n",
    "import subprocess\n",
    "import threading\n",
    "import time\n",
    "import requests\n",
    "import json\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"🚀 启动PonyTown游戏服务器...\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 启动游戏服务器 (后台运行)\n",
    "def start_game_server():\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        subprocess.run([\n",
    "            'npm', 'start'\n",
    "        ], cwd='/content/pony-town-ready', check=True)\n",
    "    except subprocess.CalledProcessError as e:\n",
    "        print(f\"❌ 服务器启动错误: {e}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 在后台线程中启动服务器\n",
    "server_thread = threading.Thread(target=start_game_server, daemon=True)\n",
    "server_thread.start()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"⏳ 等待服务器启动... (15秒)\")\n",
    "time.sleep(15)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 启动ngrok隧道\n",
    "print(\"🌐 创建ngrok公网隧道...\")\n",
    "ngrok_process = subprocess.Popen([\n",
    "    '/content/ngrok', 'http', '8090', '--log=stdout'\n",
    "], stdout=subprocess.PIPE, stderr=subprocess.PIPE, text=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"⏳ 等待ngrok隧道建立... (10秒)\")\n",
    "time.sleep(10)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 获取ngrok公网URL\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    response = requests.get('http://localhost:4040/api/tunnels')\n",
    "    tunnels = response.json()\n",
    "    public_url = tunnels['tunnels'][0]['public_url']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\n",
    "    print(\"🎉 PonyTown游戏已成功部署到公网！\")\n",
    "    print(\"=\"*60)\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n🌐 游戏访问地址: {public_url}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n🔐 TestPony一键登录: {public_url}/auth/local/68acdc3543a9ff7ce48a3daa\")\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n📋 标准登录页面: {public_url}/mock-login.html\")\n",
    "    print(\"\\n🎮 测试账户信息:\")\n",
    "    print(\"   - 账户ID: 68acdc3543a9ff7ce48a3daa\")\n",
    "    print(\"   - 角色名: TestPony\")\n",
    "    print(\"   - 密码: test\")\n",
    "    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\n",
    "    print(\"✨ 点击上面的链接开始游戏！\")\n",
    "    print(\"📱 支持手机和电脑浏览器访问\")\n",
    "    print(\"⏰ 隧道将保持活跃直到Colab会话结束\")\n",
    "    print(\"=\"*60)\n",
    "    \n",
    "except Exception as e:\n",
    "    print(f\"❌ 获取ngrok URL失败: {e}\")\n",
    "    print(\"🔧 请检查ngrok日志或重新运行此单元格\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n🎯 游戏服务器正在运行中...\")\n",
    "print(\"💡 提示: 保持此Colab会话开启以维持游戏服务\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "id": "step6"
   },
   "source": [
    "## 步骤6：监控服务状态 (可选)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {
    "id": "monitor-status"
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 📊 监控服务状态\n",
    "import requests\n",
    "import time\n",
    "\n",
    "def check_service_status():\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        # 检查本地服务器\n",
    "        local_response = requests.get('http://localhost:8090', timeout=5)\n",
    "        local_status = \"✅ 运行中\" if local_response.status_code == 200 else \"❌ 异常\"\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 检查ngrok隧道\n",
    "        tunnels_response = requests.get('http://localhost:4040/api/tunnels', timeout=5)\n",
    "        tunnels = tunnels_response.json()\n",
    "        if tunnels['tunnels']:\n",
    "            public_url = tunnels['tunnels'][0]['public_url']\n",
    "            tunnel_status = \"✅ 活跃\"\n",
    "        else:\n",
    "            public_url = \"未找到\"\n",
    "            tunnel_status = \"❌ 断开\"\n",
    "        \n",
    "        print(f\"🎮 PonyTown服务器: {local_status}\")\n",
    "        print(f\"🌐 ngrok隧道: {tunnel_status}\")\n",
    "        print(f\"🔗 公网地址: {public_url}\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "        if public_url != \"未找到\":\n",
    "            print(f\"\\n🚀 快速链接:\")\n",
    "            print(f\"   游戏主页: {public_url}\")\n",
    "            print(f\"   一键登录: {public_url}/auth/local/68acdc3543a9ff7ce48a3daa\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "    except Exception as e:\n",
    "        print(f\"❌ 状态检查失败: {e}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"📊 服务状态检查:\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 30)\n",
    "check_service_status()"
   ]
  },
